title: Dungeon Siege III Complete Mac
description:
Dungeon Siege 3 Complete for Mac


System requirements :
Operating system : MacOsX 10.6x
Processor : Intel Core 2 Duo 2,5 GHz or better
RAM: 2 GB
Hard drive space : 5.7 GB


Tested on these

iMacWhite  - Intel Core Duo
             ATI Radeon 1600
             10.6x
             Works flawless but very slow.

iMacSilver - Intel Core 2 Duo
             GTX 880
             10.9x
             Works flawless kinda ok on lowest quality.

iMacSilver - I7
             GTX 660
             10.8x
             Works flawless on Highest quality.

iMacSilver - I7
             GTX 660
             10.9x
             Works flawless on Highest quality.


Game includes;

1. Treasures of the Sun DLC
2. Burning Band of Scorch DLC
3. Talisman of the Grand Mage DLC
4. Sacred Heart of the Legion DLC
5. Bite of Arakun DLC
